data.description: Wonderful 2.44 acres with triple wide 1911 sq ft mobile home. Very open floor plan, living rm & dining rm. Family rm off kitchen. 3 big bedrms,1.75 baths. Primary suite w/walk in closet & .75 bath w/2 sinks & large shower. Country kitchen w/eating area. Wood stove & laminate flooring. Huge covered back deck w/lower deck & hot tub. MIL w/bath rm, washer, dryer & tankless H2O. RV parking w/hookups.36x24 3 car garage & 28x36 shop finished w/loft & AC. Both buildings also have carports on the ends for even more covered parking! Pond, pastures, fruit trees, walnut trees, garden, small barn & outbuildings! Country atmosphere yet only 10 mins to town! Septic and Highland public water. So much property, buildings, parking and privacy for the money!
